summary: An abode i created to hold all my little Dwemer robot minions, that i obtained through another mod.
descriptionHtml:
A Dwemer Outpost, 
Contains cooking and so on...
Only actually lightly furnished,
Treasury, where you can toss all those colored gems into basins... Or at least if you want to...
You have to find it, though I did place a marker on the map...
Watch out for Dragons, Giants or anything else nearby.
Was going to make a quest, but wasn\\\'t sure how to and didn\\\'t feel like it.

Suggestions problems contact me here...at the Nexus.
author: celethiel
